# Priority Scoring Rules

- Score each validated finding on a 0-100 scale using weighted factors:
  - Strategic relevance (30)
  - Commercial impact (25)
  - Evidence quality (20)
  - Competitive urgency (15)
  - 30-day actionability (10)
- Apply priority bands:
  - 80-100: High
  - 60-79: Medium
  - 0-59: Low
- Rank findings by score and present top 3 strategic moves only.
- Archive low-priority noise unless repeated patterns emerge.
